To set the client secret as an environment variable (substituting <SECRET> with the actual client secret), enter:

SECRET=<SECRET>

After that, you can execute the GET-token-demo script by entering:
eval `CLIENT_SECRET=$SECRET ./GET-token-demo`

To set up the oidc-agent to use the ILDG IAM's public client, enter:
eval `oidc-agent`
CLIENT_SECRET=$SECRET ./oidc-public_client-conf.sh 